Dialogue: 9,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are the four of us being shaken around on this bus?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that, of course, lies in this bus's destination.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its final stop, Zaizen Village, is famous for mountain hiking and hot springs.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going for the hot springs, not the hiking.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:26.87,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I'd much rather be taking a break from everything during my summer "break", however...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:31.79,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for helping me with my uncle, Oreki-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all take a trip to the hot springs together?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Let's go...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be coming by to pick us up any time now.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really great view.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's typical Houtarou for you. Already complaining.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only one and a half hours.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, good job getting us these rooms, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:03.78,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My relatives are in the middle of renovating their inn and can't take guests, so they're letting us stay for free.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:13.21,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Oreki-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! We're here!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki, hurry up or we're leaving you there.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! Our inn!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Seizansou.
