Dialogue: 9,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the elder sister, Zenna Rie,
Dialogue: 9,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is her younger sister, Zenna Kayo.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in fourth and sixth grades.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure grown—
Dialogue: 9,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rooms are the last two on the second floor.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou! Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room has a great view!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this kind of thing isn't bad every now and then.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:55.63,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I think it would have been more dignified to come alone.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, traveling alone?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:05.26,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you're here because Chitanda planned it and Mayaka had connections.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for dinner!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cheese?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stew.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gratin.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese fondue.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chilled shabushabu?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's dessert too.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it cheesecake?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could smell it.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like Maya-neechan said!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell them, Ibara?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play with fireworks tomorrow!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Dad bought some yesterday and—
Dialogue: 9,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:57.02,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you burn yourself?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful next time.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Satoshi already head to the bath?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is a hot springs inn, after all...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed to?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same place you are.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ibara?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids took her somewhere.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.48,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a bit random, but what kind of person is your sister?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seriously is random...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:42.23,0:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, you're an only child, aren't you?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call her an oddball, and you could call her a genius.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that I could be better than her at anything.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've never really cared to be.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why my sister all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of the Zenna sisters?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:06.21,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I've always wanted a sibling.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An older sister or a younger brother...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:11.05,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's wonderful to have someone you can go to for anything always there for you?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this young lady is far too optimistic.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks her dreams are true for everyone.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having siblings in reality isn't wonderful in the slightest.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this isn't a mixed bath...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than I thought...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bath is great!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's practically flowing through my body!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:21.62,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting your blood diluted with water is dangerous.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you think of something more interesting to say?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.96,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it shows you're relaxing.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki?!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath made him dizzy.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of pathetic, really.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:12.72,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't even been in there half as long as me, but when I turned around, he'd almost passed out.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fated never to enjoy an event.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm still sick from that bus ride.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel awful.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki-san? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still hot...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get a cold towel for you?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to sleep.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you worry when we're out on a trip like this...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, we're going to tell ghost stories in a bit.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:23.83,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling better, you're welcome to join us.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you feel better soon.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even eight yet...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drums?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:48.19,0:09:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we don't really need the annex.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the window next door is open, too...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This inn has a secret.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, a gloomy customer came to stay.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was put in room seven in the main building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.66,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(110,0)\blur1\fs50\c&H002332&\frz6.328\pos(607.857,301.286)}7
Dialogue: 9,0:10:05.66,0:10:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told them, "I don't need meals or room service. Just stay away."
Dialogue: 9,0:10:10.96,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he'd already paid in advance, and it was the busy season, so he was a perfect guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:15.55,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.3\fad(0,0)\blur1\fs50\c&H002332&\frz6.328\frx356\fry338\pos(950.257,285.286)}7
Dialogue: 9,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that evening, a piercing scream echoed throughout the inn.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scream?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:21.76,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guest in room seven had hanged himself, and his body was swaying in the wind.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.18,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he had embezzled money from his company and run away.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:34.40,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that incident, guests staying in room seven all say the same thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.82,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,460)\blur1\fs35\c&H102F38&\frz12.13\move(934.533,516.533,962.533,515.199,27,1320)}2
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.95,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's something in this room. I see shadows at night."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.32,Open,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,460)\blur1\fs35\c&H123245&\frz12.13\move(820,266,848,264,27,1320)}3
