Dialogue: 9,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the ninth guest in that room...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:49.46,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the night, he suddenly succumbed to an unknown illness!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.00,0:10:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:56.46,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Grandma asked for an exorcism and had the annex built.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to stop any bad rumors from spreading.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this room seven?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it right across from this window.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That room there.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:10.73,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We live on the first floor, and we're told to stay away from the second floor.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. You're joking.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone I told you, okay?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that one before.
