Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.00,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(636,349.733)\fad(250,0)\b1\c&H030004&\fscx151\fscy156}Hyouka
Dialogue: 9,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what, now?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I woke up in the middle of the night...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.19,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I turned over, in the room across from ours, I saw a hanged shadow swaying back and forth!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rare to see Ibara panicking like this.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad you're not here to see it, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the bath?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was absolutely wonderful!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.21,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fay-0.5\fs50\fnBurst My Bubble\b0\c&H1E2A2F&\pos(719.682,388.349)}Rie{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.46,Handwriting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay-0.1\blur1\fs150\fnBurst My Bubble\b1\c&H222525&\pos(564.025,355.892)}Rie{\b0}
Dialogue: 9,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wasn't your futon nice and soft?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I slept wonderfully!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Kayo didn't write hers.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:27.01,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were scared of stories like that, Maya-neechan.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm scared of ghosts!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you see something like that...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just disturbing!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-neechan... You saw it?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it. I definitely saw it. I really saw it!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan! You told them that story?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said not to tell anyone!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:46.78,0:12:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. It's just Maya-neechan.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of Mayaka-san's story?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hanged shadow?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:03.88,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's one of those things that every inn probably has.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you think what Mayaka-san says is true?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps I'm mistaken as well.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it too. A hanged shadow.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mayaka-san woke up, I did too.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw it swaying in the dark.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:32.49,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was mistaken, but Mayaka-san said she saw the same thing...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably just mistook something else for it.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Satoshi was saying yesterday, "The ghost, when examined..."
Dialogue: 9,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...was just withered flowers"?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:46.38,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did I see?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what it was we saw, then.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I—
Dialogue: 9,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look into it!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Rie that I would help her with her homework!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discover the truth behind this mystery!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:12.91,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, if I have to do it, make it quick.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.16,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{overlap}Excuse us.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:17.25,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so you saw this hanged shadow in the room across from yours?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How big was it?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was neither particularly big nor small.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the shape?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember very well.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about color?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. It was just a shadow.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it looked like a human shadow against the light.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the light...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was night, so the only light source would have been the moon.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon was quite bright last night.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that related—
Dialogue: 9,0:14:50.15,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda, when did you stop telling stories and go to bed?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were the shutters at the time?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they were closed.
Dialogue: 9,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the shutters were closed, there couldn't have been a shadow.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is becoming a hassle...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably best to go to the main building and take a look at room seven.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful! So mysterious!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we took this trip!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we hadn't.
